## Booking & Scheduling (booking-mcp)

### Bookable Event Lead Times
| Event Type | Min Lead Time |
|---|---|
| Buyer on-site visit | 24 hours |
| Third-party inspection | 48 hours |
| Lab sample collection | 72 hours |
| Live auction session | 7 days |
| Mediation meeting | 48 hours |
| Re-weigh appointment | 24 hours |

- Buffer before/after each booking: 30 minutes (configurable).
- Reminders sent at: 24h, 2h, and 30min before the event.
- No-show tracking: repeated no-shows trigger `dispute_mcp.platform_integrity_scores` penalty.
- Cancellation policy: full refund >24h, 50% refund 12–24h, no refund <12h.
- All times stored in UTC; display in user's local timezone.

### Calendar Integrations
Two-way sync supported: Google Calendar (OAuth2), Microsoft Outlook (Office 365 API), Apple Calendar (ICS).
Conflict detection runs against all connected calendars before confirming a booking.

