## Material Grading Standards
| Category | Standard | Key Parameters |
|---|---|---|
| Ferrous Metals | ISRI Specifications (HMS 1, HMS 2) | Density, composition, contamination, size |
| Non-Ferrous Metals | ISRI + LME Grade Standards | Purity, alloy type, weight, visual quality |
| Plastics | ASTM D7611 Resin Identification | Resin type, color, contamination, form |
| Paper & Cardboard | ISRI Paper Stock Guidelines | Grade, moisture, contamination, bale weight |
| E-Waste | R2/e-Stewards Certification | Component type, precious metal content, hazmat |
| Construction | CSA Standards | Composition, size, contamination |

Mandatory inspection thresholds: optional for listings > $25K, mandatory for listings > $100K.

