## Mobile App Architecture (React Native)
- Framework: React Native + Expo, React Navigation, Zustand + React Query
- Offline-first: WatermelonDB for local SQLite storage; background sync when connectivity returns
- Camera-first workflows: photo capture for listings, scale tickets, inspection reports, POD
- Push notifications: Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) / APNs
- Biometric auth: Face ID / Touch ID via Expo Local Authentication
- GPS: Expo Location for delivery tracking and geofencing
- Sync conflict resolution: last-write-wins with manual merge UI for conflicts
